# ------------------------------------------------------------------
# HeartWire OS — Git LFS tracking
# ------------------------------------------------------------------
# Large or binary assets are stored via Git LFS so the working repo
# stays small and GitHub's 100MB-per-file push limit is respected.
#
# NOTE on LFS quotas (as of 2026):
#   - Free tier: 1 GB storage + 1 GB bandwidth / month.
#   - Data Packs: $5/mo each for +50 GB storage and +50 GB bandwidth.
#   - The current HeartWire OS working tree holds ~3.75 GB of
#     LFS-tracked binaries (see core/MIGRATION-STATUS.md), so budget
#     at least 1 Data Pack before the first push.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------

# Documents (textbooks, slides, handouts) ---------------------------
*.pdf    filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
*.ppt    filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
